TITLE: Operation Object Example in YAML
DESCRIPTION: YAML representation of the Operation Object example showing user signup configuration with all available fields.
SOURCE: https://github.com/asyncapi/spec/blob/master/spec/asyncapi.md#2025-04-22_snippet_28

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
title: User sign up
summary: Action to sign a user up.
description: A longer description
